curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/1477' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2021", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2021 is a low power and low dropout voltage  RF linear regulator. It is capable of supplying 300mA  output current with typical dropout voltage of only  270mV. The operating input voltage range is from 2.5V  to 5.5V. The fixed output voltage range is from 0.9V to  5.0V.  Other features include output current limit and thermal  shutdown protection.  The SGM2021 is available in a Green SOT-23-3 package.  It operates over an operating temperature range of  -40℃ to +85℃.    "}'
